string.text: An in-depth examination of major international news, events and current affairs with an emphasis on American news.
President Trump has threatened to hit China with 104% tariffs. Newsnight hears from a Trump economic insider and a US business owner calling for an end to the trade war. With Victoria Derbyshire.
An in-depth examination of major international news, events and current affairs with an emphasis on American news.
